title: 199.Lives.The.Travis.Pastrana.Story.2008.DVDR-GRZYBO
description:
This new documentary "199 Lives" will go beyond the all the films, the ridiculously insane stunts and provide the world a glimpse into his life from childhood to his motocross racing career, his dominance in FMX, and the injuries that almost ended his career. Few of us are as extreme as Travis pastrana, whether it is base jumping, sky diving, FMX double back flips, rally car racing, crashing cars, or stunts in his foam pit. At the age 22, Travis Pastrana is an action sports phenomenon.

* Winner of Best Film at the 2008 X-Dance Film Festival



KEEP GOING TRAVIS !



 - GRZYBO
